{"tid":1952970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅二代難躲瘟疫   共軍副司令之子感染武漢肺炎死亡","createTime":"2020-04-01T02:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T02:15:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d283e4866b9e58ba02633d7283b610ece4f6e8","tid":1952970,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:04:25.000Z","msg":"病毒面前人人平等，不認官階、身分、財富。近日陸媒披露，有中共原湖北省軍區副司令員戴克明將軍之子戴方明感染中共病毒，2月在武漢天佑醫院去世。另外，儘管中共高層多次召開視頻會議，強調死守北京，盡最大可能切斷中共病毒（武漢肺炎）傳染源，有消息稱，這瘟疫早已經攻入北京機關大院，有中共紅二代也被確診感染。<br />\n <br />\n近日，陸媒《紅船雜誌》引述知情人士的話披露，中共原湖北省軍區副司令員戴克明將軍之子戴方明（又名戴曉明），因感染中共病毒去世。<br />\n <br />\n報道說，戴方明染病半個多月後突然惡化，於2月10日在武漢天佑醫院去世，終年71歲。戴去世後，其夫人周芳也因感染在搶救中。<br />\n <br />\n據悉，戴方明於1968年12月在中共軍隊高炮63師服役，歷任排長、連長。1974年因傷轉業在武漢市糧食局科研所任科長。湖北紅軍精神研究專業委員會會員。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-03-31/27715623\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020-03-31%2F27715623&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=4a3cd33d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-03-31/27715623</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/03/123-600x324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F123-600x324.jpg&h=d35d71dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4c988ba9c9b43fcad6d54409e9a2e8b240809f9","tid":1952970,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:05:56.000Z","msg":"白頭人送黑頭人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f84632b147d1b4fc53ea088cc6139622a41885c","tid":1952970,"uid":224882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:07:05.000Z","msg":"最緊要一家人齊齊整整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301d095f66c7b435556237ad1b7bdce8fcf4d1d5","tid":1952970,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"有消息稱，這瘟疫早已經攻入北京機關大院，有中共紅二代也被確診感染。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n落去見毛主席"},{"pid":"a380dce57910707f63ecc09d4506be005310fe66","tid":1952970,"uid":254788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"死得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359bc5bd0e0c59f366b367ecb9d5e21e8f8547fd","tid":1952970,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Wrmycj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Wrmycj.gif&h=fb2681d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dd007c1d2b8fdd6e1501a2fe9bede0b7ed2745a","tid":1952970,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4c988ba9c9b43fcad6d54409e9a2e8b240809f9","tid":1952970,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:05:56.000Z","msg":"白頭人送黑頭人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:08:27.000Z","msg":"68年服役，條友最少70啦仲黑頭人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係白頭人送白頭人"},{"pid":"8d7e0c355319b9dd815ad02017f5c9bfe3e2d9d8","tid":1952970,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Yv7UyJPNJps/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FYv7UyJPNJps%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=3ac527c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c1b24acdf894cb3fe52b2592a38560e2e738238","tid":1952970,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:15:14.000Z","msg":"可以宣傳習大帝, <br />\n無好好防護疫情令其子死亡.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}